ğŸ“Š 9. Development vs Production

| Feature    | Development | Production      |
| ---------- | ----------- | --------------- |
| Logging    | Basic       | Detailed        |
| Monitoring | Manual      | AgentOps        |
| Debugging  | Console     | Structured logs |
| Scaling    | Local       | Managed         |

